OL,3,CGlasgow will host scaled-down
OL,4,CCommonwealth Games in 2026, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Scottish government has agreed to
OL,8,Fsupport Glasgow in hosting a scaled-
OL,9,Fdown version of the Commonwealth Games
OL,10,Fin 2026.
OL,12,FIn April, Commonwealth Games Scotland
OL,13,Fannounced a "cost-effective" plan to
OL,14,Fhost the Games after Victoria,
OL,15,FAustralia, withdrew as host in July
OL,16,F2023.
