OL,3,CGlasgow will host scaled-down
OL,4,CCommonwealth Games in 2026, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Australian state of Victoria
OL,8,Fwithdrew due to rising estimated
OL,9,Fcosts, leaving Glasgow, which last
OL,10,Fhosted the event in 2014, to once
OL,11,Fagain welcome athletes from
OL,12,FCommonwealth nations.
OL,14,FThe plan has reportedly been approved
OL,15,Fby the Scottish government, paving the
OL,16,Fway for Glasgow to be officially
OL,17,Fconfirmed as the host in the coming
OL,18,Fweeks.
