OL,3,CGlasgow will host scaled-down
OL,4,CCommonwealth Games in 2026, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt is understood that the 2026 Games
OL,8,Fwill feature around 10 to 13 sports,
OL,9,Fcompared to 19 at the 2022 Games in
OL,10,FBirmingham.
OL,12,FDue to a lack of time and funding,
OL,13,Fsome sports will have to be dropped
OL,14,Ffrom the multi-event Games.
OL,16,FScottish Health Secretary Neil Gray
OL,17,Fsaid: "The Scottish Government has
OL,18,Fconducted a thorough assessment of
OL,19,FCommonwealth Games Scotland's proposal
OL,20,Ffor Glasgow to host the 2026
OL,21,FCommonwealth Games.
