OL,3,CGlasgow will host scaled-down
OL,4,CCommonwealth Games in 2026, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Commonwealth Games Federation is
OL,8,Fproviding around #100 million in
OL,9,Ffunding, while Commonwealth Games
OL,10,FAustralia will contribute part of its
OL,11,Fcompensation from the cancelled
OL,12,FVictoria Games to support hosting the
OL,13,Fevent in Glasgow.
OL,15,FThe multi-sport event is held every
OL,16,Ffour years across Commonwealth
OL,17,Fcountries, with Birmingham the most
OL,18,Frecent host city in 2022.
OL,20,FEdinburgh staged the Games in 1970 and
OL,21,F1986.
